column4: 1. I am familiar with the concept of big data in e-commerce.
column5: 2. I believe that big data analytics improves my online shopping experience.
column6: 3. I believe that big data helps me find products more quickly when shopping online.
column7: 4.  I feel that big data analytics enables me to discover better deals and discounts while shopping online.
column8: 5.   I believe that big data analytics improves the accuracy of search results on e-commerce platforms.
column9: 6.    I believe that big data analytics enhances the personalization of my online shopping experience.
column10: 7. I think big data analytics improves the ease of comparing products and prices between e-commerce platforms.
column11: 8. I think big data analytics makes it easier for me to receive relevant product recommendations.
column12: 9. I feel that big data analytics reduces the complexity of finding what I need on e-commerce platforms.
column13: 10. I find that e-commerce platforms using big data analytics reduce the effort required to find relevant deals and offers.
column14: 11. I feel confident using e-commerce platforms with big data analytics, even without technical expertise.
column15: 12. I am concerned that my online shopping behaviours is being tracked and analyzed by e-commerce platforms using big data analytics.
column16: 13. I feel confident that e-commerce platforms using big data analytics have strong encryption methods to protect my personal information.
column17: 14. I am worried that e-commerce platforms may share my personal data with third parties through the use of big data analytics.
column18: 15. I am concerned that e-commerce platforms using big data analytics may not notify me if a data breach event occurs.
column19: 16. I feel uncomfortable when ads based on my shopping behaviours on e-commerce platforms appear on other social media applications.
column20: 17. I believe that e-commerce platforms using big data analytics should conduct regular security audits to ensure the safety of my data.
column21: 18. I am concerned that e-commerce platforms use big data analytics to collect more personal data which is unnecessary for my shopping experience.
column22: 19. I am concerned that big data analytics might be used to track my online transfer details and payment information on e-commerce platforms.
column23: 20. I believe that e-commerce platforms should allow me to request them to stop collecting my personal data.
column24: 21. I prefer e-commerce platforms that implement big data analytics.
column25: 22. I believe big data analytics is beneficial to the e-commerce industry.
column26: 23. I feel that big data analytics has helped e-commerce platforms understand customer needs better.
column27: 24. I think the benefits of big data analytics in e-commerce outweigh its potential risks.
column28: 25. I would recommend e-commerce platforms that use big data analytics to my family and friends.
